{
  "id": "6413dacd0088fe001cb9d74f",
  "title": "等価変換理論",
  "created": 1679022798,
  "updated": 1679054349,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6413dacd0088fe001cb9d74f",
      "text": "等価変換理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679022798,
      "updated": 1679022823
    },
    {
      "id": "6413dacdaff09e00002f36a0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9bf1823e974bad23dd77e7b8717490ad]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679022798,
      "updated": 1679022818
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb598",
      "text": "[https://www.jcdc.jp/等価変換理論について/等価変換理論展開の定義/ ■等価変換理論展開の定義 - 特定非営利活動法人 日本創造力開発センター]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb599",
      "text": "\t>Ａο－原系(出発系)の中の具体的事象の一つ(クリアすべき課題､または他のモデル)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb59a",
      "text": " > Ｂτ－変換系(到達系)に出現した事象(発明､開発の完成)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb59b",
      "text": " > vi－観点(ものを見るときの角度や立場､考え方の方向性:開発目的に合った観点を1つ選ぶ)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb59c",
      "text": " > ε－ひとつの観点のもとで､Ａοから抽出した抽象的な要素(物事の核心､願望の中心)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb59d",
      "text": " > c－抽象的要素に具体性を与える限定条件",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb59e",
      "text": " > cε－具体化された開発の核心をなす概念(アイデア)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb59f",
      "text": " > Σa－原系の特殊な条件群(モデルの中の不要な要素､開発時には廃棄の対象)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "641455dfaff09e00000eb5a0",
      "text": " > Σb－変換系の特殊な条件群(開発時に新たに必要となる要素､導入の対象)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679054304,
      "updated": 1679054304
    },
    {
      "id": "64144175aff09e00000eb58c",
      "text": "\t数式だと思わない方がいい、これは絵",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049077,
      "updated": 1679049078
    },
    {
      "id": "64144176aff09e00000eb58d",
      "text": " まあ「構造式」も図なので「式」が「数式」だとは限らないよね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049078,
      "updated": 1679049078
    },
    {
      "id": "64144176aff09e00000eb58e",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/589387a08ddf468f9866f72caf3b1c7e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049078,
      "updated": 1679049110
    },
    {
      "id": "64144195aff09e00000eb58f",
      "text": "\t\tこれの方がわかりやすい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049109,
      "updated": 1679049127
    },
    {
      "id": "64144195aff09e00000eb590",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049109,
      "updated": 1679049109
    },
    {
      "id": "6413dae1aff09e00002f36a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679022818,
      "updated": 1679054300
    },
    {
      "id": "64141221aff09e00007d037f",
      "text": "https://www.jcdc.jp/等価変換理論について/等価変換理論の解説/第1回-創造理論の系譜-等価変換理論のできた経緯-理論の概要/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679036961,
      "updated": 1679036962
    },
    {
      "id": "64141221aff09e00007d0380",
      "text": "\t下記はいずれもアナロジー思考を重視していた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679036961,
      "updated": 1679044953
    },
    {
      "id": "64143102aff09e00000eb572",
      "text": " \t[市川亀久彌]「[独創的研究の方法論]」（1944 年）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679044867,
      "updated": 1679044911
    },
    {
      "id": "64143107aff09e00000eb574",
      "text": " \t[ポリア]「[いかにして問題を解くか]」（1945 年）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679044871,
      "updated": 1679044914
    },
    {
      "id": "6414310baff09e00000eb575",
      "text": " \t[ウエルトハイマー]「[生産的思考]」（1945 年）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679044875,
      "updated": 1679044916
    },
    {
      "id": "64143119aff09e00000eb577",
      "text": "\t同時期ロシアにおいて、アウトシューラーによる問題解法手法 [TRIZ] が誕生していた（1946 年）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679044891,
      "updated": 1679044919
    },
    {
      "id": "64143137aff09e00000eb578",
      "text": "\t市川氏「アナロジーが原理的に模倣的思考なのに、なぜ新概念の創造に結びつくのか？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679044919,
      "updated": 1679045273
    },
    {
      "id": "6414316faff09e00000eb57c",
      "text": "\t1955年「[等価変換思考方法]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679044976,
      "updated": 1679052795
    },
    {
      "id": "641432b4aff09e00000eb580",
      "text": "\t「創造的思考の本質は、相異なる対象の、一方もしくは双方を観念的に加工して、適当な思考観点を導入し、両者に共通する様々な側面 ( 等価性 ) を、できるだけ多く見つけ出す思考パターンによってきめられる」（「創造性研究第 1 集」1964 年、誠信書房、p.20）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679045301,
      "updated": 1679045327
    },
    {
      "id": "64143102aff09e00000eb573",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679044867,
      "updated": 1679044867
    },
    {
      "id": "6414331faff09e00000eb587",
      "text": "「等価性」は「[体験過程と意味の創造]」で「二つの意味の間に『[経験の側面]』が見つかる」といってたものに関連してそう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679045408,
      "updated": 1679054349
    },
    {
      "id": "6413dd6faff09e00002f36ac",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/aba57ec6821fcdd802c29075aa93b5dd]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679023472,
      "updated": 1679045497
    },
    {
      "id": "6413dd70aff09e00002f36ae",
      "text": "　こういうことかな？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679023472,
      "updated": 1679052774
    },
    {
      "id": "64144940aff09e0000a8f0ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051072,
      "updated": 1679051073
    },
    {
      "id": "64145023aff09e000064e5c6",
      "text": "https://www.jcdc.jp/等価変換理論について/等価変換理論の解説/第%EF%BC%92回等価方程式とフローチャート/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052835,
      "updated": 1679052836
    },
    {
      "id": "64145024aff09e000064e5c8",
      "text": " アナロジーが表面的な特徴に偏りがちなことを批判している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052836,
      "updated": 1679052836
    },
    {
      "id": "64145024aff09e000064e5c9",
      "text": " 　抽象化をどうやるかという話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052836,
      "updated": 1679052836
    },
    {
      "id": "64145024aff09e000064e5ca",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/589387a08ddf468f9866f72caf3b1c7e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052836,
      "updated": 1679052836
    },
    {
      "id": "64145024aff09e000064e5cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052836,
      "updated": 1679052836
    },
    {
      "id": "64145024aff09e000064e5cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052837,
      "updated": 1679052837
    },
    {
      "id": "64145023aff09e000064e5c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052835,
      "updated": 1679052835
    },
    {
      "id": "6413dd70aff09e00002f36ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679023472,
      "updated": 1679052864
    },
    {
      "id": "641441c4aff09e00000eb591",
      "text": "フローチャート",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049157,
      "updated": 1679049158
    },
    {
      "id": "64145012aff09e000064e5c5",
      "text": "\tアナロジーの過程をもっと詳細に言語化して意識的に実行できるようにしようと考えたのかな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052819,
      "updated": 1679052820
    },
    {
      "id": "641434eeaff09e00000e3491",
      "text": "\t出発系Aをどうやって探索するか、という話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679045871,
      "updated": 1679049158
    },
    {
      "id": "641442c8aff09e0000e16141",
      "text": "\t「観点」とは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049416,
      "updated": 1679049445
    },
    {
      "id": "641442e4aff09e0000e16142",
      "text": "\t　「解決の方向」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049445,
      "updated": 1679049457
    },
    {
      "id": "641442f5aff09e0000e16143",
      "text": "\t　「[見る方向によって重なって見える]」の「見る方向」かと思ったが違うようだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049461,
      "updated": 1679049538
    },
    {
      "id": "6414353faff09e00000e3493",
      "text": "\t「問題の本質」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679045951,
      "updated": 1679049610
    },
    {
      "id": "64144381aff09e00000eb592",
      "text": "\t\t「観点を動詞化する」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049601,
      "updated": 1679049627
    },
    {
      "id": "6414439caff09e00000eb595",
      "text": "\t\t\t興味深い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049629,
      "updated": 1679049638
    },
    {
      "id": "641443bbaff09e0000e16144",
      "text": "\t\t　「[名詞形より動詞形]」と似た発想だ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049659,
      "updated": 1679049681
    },
    {
      "id": "64144948aff09e0000a8f0ef",
      "text": "\tあー、なるほど。これは「[どうやって、どうなる]」だな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051081,
      "updated": 1679051099
    },
    {
      "id": "64144384aff09e00000eb593",
      "text": "　\t[https://gyazo.com/309d7ef2625c08795c51ff7cec7f69c7]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679049604,
      "updated": 1679051100
    },
    {
      "id": "64144922aff09e00000eb597",
      "text": "　　[何がどうなるとよい？]には答えられるが、それを実現するための「どうやって」がわからないシチュエーション",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051043,
      "updated": 1679051145
    },
    {
      "id": "64144989aff09e0000a8f0f0",
      "text": "　　「どうなる」を含んでる事例を探す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051146,
      "updated": 1679051156
    },
    {
      "id": "64144995aff09e0000a8f0f1",
      "text": "　　その事例の「どうやって」部分から、関係のない特徴を削ぎ落とす",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051158,
      "updated": 1679051269
    },
    {
      "id": "6414503caff09e000064e5cd",
      "text": "　　それから、問題領域の特徴を付け加える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052860,
      "updated": 1679052868
    },
    {
      "id": "64145044aff09e000064e5ce",
      "text": "   抽象化して、応用する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052869,
      "updated": 1679052871
    },
    {
      "id": "64145045aff09e000064e5cf",
      "text": "   \t畑村洋太郎の[登って降りるメタファー]だね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052869,
      "updated": 1679052871
    },
    {
      "id": "64144a21aff09e0000a8f0f3",
      "text": "　　図でPと書いたのは、PDCAのP",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051297,
      "updated": 1679051313
    },
    {
      "id": "64144a30aff09e0000a8f0f4",
      "text": "　　 [最初のPをどう生み出すのか]の方法の一つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051313,
      "updated": 1679051365
    },
    {
      "id": "64145076aff09e0000a8f0fd",
      "text": "　　 　時期的にPDCAサイクルはまだ生まれてないので〜",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052918,
      "updated": 1679052932
    },
    {
      "id": "64144a65aff09e0000a8f0f5",
      "text": "　　 アナロジーではこのプロセスを特に言語化されてない1ステップにしてる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051365,
      "updated": 1679051380
    },
    {
      "id": "64144b9baff09e0000a8f0f7",
      "text": "　　 それを言語化してステップに分けたことを指して「アナロジーではない」と言ってる？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051675,
      "updated": 1679051860
    },
    {
      "id": "64144c54aff09e0000a8f0fc",
      "text": "　　 アナロジーが言語化されてない方法によって類似性を扱うから、見た目の類似などの表層的な類似に偏りがち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051860,
      "updated": 1679051897
    },
    {
      "id": "6414508aaff09e0000a8f0fe",
      "text": "　　　ステップを言語化して意識的に行うことで偏りをなくそうとしたか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679052938,
      "updated": 1679052968
    },
    {
      "id": "64144a82aff09e0000a8f0f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051394,
      "updated": 1679051409
    },
    {
      "id": "64144917aff09e00000eb596",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679051031,
      "updated": 1679051031
    },
    {
      "id": "641435e7aff09e00000eb58a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679046119,
      "updated": 1679052827
    }
  ]
}